  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique is a more advanced version of the Glimmer Dragon technique. Until the end of your next turn, whenever a creature would score a critical hit against you, including the critical hit that triggered this Jutsu, that attack's damage is reduced to 0. Each time an attack is prevented this way, you may expend a Ki Die to make an attack against them or cast a Gouken Hijutsu or Taijutsu of C-Rank or lower that only targets them.</p><p><strong>Empower:</strong> When you would make an attack from this Jutsu, you may expend a Ki Die, rolling it and adding the result to the attack roll.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank above B-Rank, this Jutsu costs 3 more chakra. At A-Rank, you may cast a Jutsu of B-Rank or lower, and at S-Rank, you may cast a Jutsu of A-Rank or lower when you deflect an attack.</p>",
